{
  "message": "fix: Remove asyncify-ignore-indirect to enable async imports through CPython's ceval\n\nCPython dispatches C extension function calls through indirect calls\n(call_indirect / function pointers) in the ceval loop. The\nasyncify-ignore-indirect flag prevented wasm-opt from instrumenting\nthese call sites, causing \"unreachable\" traps when async host imports\n(KV, R2, D1, HTTP) triggered Asyncify stack unwinding.\n\nWithout instrumentation at the indirect call sites, the unwind path\nhits an unreachable instruction instead of properly saving the stack.\nThis is why all async imports failed while sync imports (env_get)\nworked fine \u2014 sync imports don't need stack unwinding.\n\nRemoving asyncify-ignore-indirect will increase WASM binary size\n(more functions instrumented) but is required for correct operation.",
  "files": [
    {
      "sha": "824149c0fb6ca192ded41853769aa36126d81f6c",
      "filename": "docs/design-do-architecture.md",
      "status": "modified",
      "additions": 0,
      "deletions": 1,
      "changes": 1,
      "blob_url": "https://github.com/teamchong/pymode/blob/8f35d0418abcf2c21a1bd1eecdbb8f9ac11ed356/docs%2Fdesign-do-architecture.md",
      "raw_url": "https://github.com/teamchong/pymode/raw/8f35d0418abcf2c21a1bd1eecdbb8f9ac11ed356/docs%2Fdesign-do-architecture.md",
      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/teamchong/pymode/contents/docs%2Fdesign-do-architecture.md?ref=8f35d0418abcf2c21a1bd1eecdbb8f9ac11ed356",
      "patch": "@@ -176,7 +176,6 @@ awaits the Promise, then the stack rewinds (restoring locals) and execution resu\n ```bash\n wasm-opt -O2 --asyncify \\\n   --pass-arg=asyncify-imports@pymode.tcp_recv,pymode.http_fetch,pymode.kv_get,... \\\n-  --pass-arg=asyncify-ignore-indirect \\\n   python.wasm -o python.wasm\n ```\n "
    },
    {
      "sha": "a525600cbdc5fe9aa4e85b07588bb45cdf6ff71c",
      "filename": "scripts/build-phase2.sh",
      "status": "modified",
      "additions": 0,
      "deletions": 1,
      "changes": 1,
      "blob_url": "https://github.com/teamchong/pymode/blob/8f35d0418abcf2c21a1bd1eecdbb8f9ac11ed356/scripts%2Fbuild-phase2.sh",
      "raw_url": "https://github.com/teamchong/pymode/raw/8f35d0418abcf2c21a1bd1eecdbb8f9ac11ed356/scripts%2Fbuild-phase2.sh",
      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/teamchong/pymode/contents/scripts%2Fbuild-phase2.sh?ref=8f35d0418abcf2c21a1bd1eecdbb8f9ac11ed356",
      "patch": "@@ -307,7 +307,6 @@ if command -v wasm-opt >/dev/null 2>&1; then\n         --enable-sign-ext \\\n         --enable-mutable-globals \\\n         --pass-arg=\"asyncify-imports@${ASYNC_IMPORTS}\" \\\n-        --pass-arg=asyncify-ignore-indirect \\\n         \"$BUILD_DIR/python.wasm\" -o \"$BUILD_DIR/python.wasm.asyncified\"\n     mv \"$BUILD_DIR/python.wasm.asyncified\" \"$BUILD_DIR/python.wasm\"\n "
    },
    {
      "sha": "454f040092f077108f4a81b16481aa6f634d9d08",
      "filename": "scripts/build-phase2.ts",
      "status": "modified",
      "additions": 0,
      "deletions": 1,
      "changes": 1,
      "blob_url": "https://github.com/teamchong/pymode/blob/8f35d0418abcf2c21a1bd1eecdbb8f9ac11ed356/scripts%2Fbuild-phase2.ts",
      "raw_url": "https://github.com/teamchong/pymode/raw/8f35d0418abcf2c21a1bd1eecdbb8f9ac11ed356/scripts%2Fbuild-phase2.ts",
      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/teamchong/pymode/contents/scripts%2Fbuild-phase2.ts?ref=8f35d0418abcf2c21a1bd1eecdbb8f9ac11ed356",
      "patch": "@@ -631,7 +631,6 @@ exec zig cc -target wasm32-wasi -E \"\\${ARGS[@]}\"\n         \"--enable-sign-ext\",\n         \"--enable-mutable-globals\",\n         `--pass-arg=asyncify-imports@${asyncImports}`,\n-        \"--pass-arg=asyncify-ignore-indirect\",\n         pythonWasm,\n         \"-o\",\n         asyncified,"
    },
    {
